statements: SELECT * FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents;
SELECT document_name, document_type FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE compliance_status = true;
SELECT document_name, document_type, compliance_status FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE document_type = 'Health & Safety';
SELECT document_name, compliance_status, created_date FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents ORDER BY created_date DESC;
SELECT document_id, document_name, compliance_status FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE compliance_status = false;
SELECT document_name, document_type FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE compliance_status = TRUE ORDER BY created_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE document_type = 'Energy Efficiency' OR document_type = 'Recycling' ORDER BY document_name ASC;
SELECT AVG(document_id) AS average_document_id FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE compliance_status = TRUE;
SELECT document_id, COUNT(*) AS document_count FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents GROUP BY compliance_status HAVING compliance_status = TRUE ORDER BY document_count DESC;

SELECT document_id, document_name, compliance_status, DATE_FORMAT(created_date, '%Y-%m-%d') AS formatted_created_date FROM Green_Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE compliance_status = FALSE ORDER BY document_name ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT document_id, document_name, compliance_status FROM GreenBuildingDocuments
SELECT * FROM BuildingOwners
SELECT document_name, date_created FROM GreenBuildingDocuments ORDER BY date_created DESC

SELECT * FROM GreenBuildingDocuments;

SELECT * FROM Building_Compliance_Documents WHERE compliance_status = true ORDER BY document_name DESC;

SELECT document_name, document_type FROM Building_Compliance_Documents JOIN Building_Details ON Building_Compliance_Documents.document_id = Building_Details.building_id WHERE Building_Details.location = 'New York';

SELECT document_name, compliance_status, location FROM Building_Compliance_Documents JOIN Building_Details ON Building_Compliance_Documents.document_id = Building_Details.building_id JOIN Regulatory_Agencies ON Regulatory_Agencies.agency_id = Building_Details.building_id;
SELECT * FROM Building_Details WHERE construction_year > 2000 AND location LIKE 'San %';

SELECT document_name, agency_name, contact_person FROM Building_Compliance_Documents JOIN Building_Details ON Building_Compliance_Documents.document_id = Building_Details.building_id JOIN Regulatory_Agencies ON Building_Details.agency_id = Regulatory_Agencies.agency_id WHERE compliance_status = true ORDER BY agency_name ASC;
